OL,3,CArmed men killed by police outside
OL,4,CIsraeli consulate in Turkey
OL,6,FTwo armed men have been killed by
OL,7,Fofficers in Istanbul, Turkey, after
OL,8,Fgunshots were heard by the Israeli
OL,9,Fconsulate building, police have said.
OL,11,FThree suspects were involved in the
OL,12,Fincident, which happened in Istanbul's
OL,13,FLevent district on Tuesday morning,
OL,14,FIstanbul Police Department said,
OL,15,Faccording to Turkish media. Two were
OL,16,Fkilled and one was injured.
OL,18,FTwo police officers were also injured
OL,19,Fin the stand-off, the statement said.
